#: includes/wpklc-admin-page.php:41 lib/class.admin_dashboard_wpklc.php:66
msgid ""
"Adds a simple captcha on the login form, the register form and the lost-"
"password form."
msgstr ""
"Ajoute un simple captcha sur le formulaire de connexion, le formulaire "
"d'inscription et le formulaire de mot de passe perdu."

#: includes/wpklc-admin-page.php:44
msgid ""
"You can choose here the captcha settings and the forms on which to display "
